---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="St. George Crossing | Who Is Abebe?">
  <header class="hero">
    <nav class="top-nav">
      <a class="logo" href="/">
        <img src="/logos/WIA.png" alt="WiA Logo" class="logo-icon" />
        <span>WHO IS ABEBE?</span>
      </a>

      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/timeline">Timeline</a>
        <a href="/documents">Documents</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>The LLC Network Behind St. George Crossing</h1>
      <div class="red-line"></div>
      <p>Research File No. 001</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="article-wrap">
    <article class="article-body">
      <ul class="thesis-list">
        <li>Abebe St George Ventures LLC is tied to multiple properties in Waynesboro.</li>
        <li>Several related Abebe entities share the same Atlanta address.</li>
        <li>Public records and local reporting point to a larger development concept called St. George Crossing.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>The Core Question</h2>

      <p>
        Who is behind St. George Crossing, and how do the connected entities,
        addresses, and property records fit together?
      </p>

      <blockquote class="report-quote">
        "At St. George Crossing, custom homes will not just be built, they'll be thoughtfully crafted..."
      </blockquote>

      <h2>Known Entities</h2>

      <table class="report-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Entity</th>
            <th>Address</th>
            <th>Connection</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Abebe St George Ventures LLC</td>
            <td>249 Milton Ave SE, Atlanta, GA</td>
            <td>Waynesboro / St. George Crossing</td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td>Abebe Ventures LLC</td>
            <td>249 Milton Ave SE, Atlanta, GA</td>
            <td>Related Abebe entity</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>